{"tid":208084,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"安歷基:巴塞要入五球令魯營的球迷興奮起來","createTime":"2017-04-19T09:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T10:44:15.000Z","uid":18279,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e27403fd4b1b8c8635fc35c0288a53d22243e42","tid":208084,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:52:08.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿喺歐聯8強次回合主場再遇祖雲達斯，需要收復首回合落後0:3嘅失地，賽前巴塞教練安歷基又畀貼士球迷，教大家點買好：「祖雲達斯肯定會爭取入1球，所以我哋要入5球，如果阿里基話佢哋入到2球，咁我哋就要入6球。大家都知道，巴塞用3分鐘就可以入3球，我希望球迷喺80分鐘後，唔好急住返屋企，邊個知最後有咩事發生？」事實上，巴塞喺16強次回合對巴黎聖日耳門前，安歷基都講過要入對方6球，開出「主其他」逆轉晉級，結果真係做到，所以佢講嘅嘢，值得大家參考下呀！"},{"pid":"36ca769c9d34ffcc01245622d7c30d0d9ce86e69","tid":208084,"uid":138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd587520738d0da8ca98fbf590bf2a8552498ccc","tid":208084,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:55:57.000Z","msg":"好明顯講比球證聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2b47ee071c8c57b6eec4a64fecda0116566b54","tid":208084,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好明顯講比球證聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我們不須要黑哨，因為體育的本質是追求更快、更高、更強，黑哨幫助唔到我地達到呢個目標。相反堅持刻苦的訓練，才能讓我地達到呢個目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb85e87e6eddfa10ffdbbdd25b660c68e0e9bc7","tid":208084,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:03:45.000Z","msg":"阿里基係屌帥？"},{"pid":"2ebf0fa928380552b8fc2b70c0f9f715181c75bc","tid":208084,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿里基係屌帥？</blockquote><br />\n安歷基更強<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5e21bc6cebba070f293171d045e70cc82b5b1f","tid":208084,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:06:56.000Z","msg":"又講定劇本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafac072b45ee68dab26a6931574e40ba81b551a","tid":208084,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又講定劇本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個即使係劇本都係上帝的劇本，係上帝給予巴塞試練的劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58867252da995f6bc30fb59c60dbdee4b443766","tid":208084,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又講定劇本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個即使係劇本都係上帝的劇本，係上帝給予巴塞試練的劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知唔知點解海係藍色 火係紅色？<br />\n因為上帝係巴塞fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e40e1f6feb94591bb762f278d7324f6b6897dd","tid":208084,"uid":87563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又講定劇本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個即使係劇本都係上帝的劇本，係上帝給予巴塞試練的劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知唔知點解海係藍色 火係紅色？<br />\n因為上帝係巴塞fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9d476b443fedd6a5abd75629208c52527b923a","tid":208084,"uid":34001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:51:51.000Z","msg":"保方嚇到賴屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9bbfddeaee9182ea4d485718dbfcea6eeca4f2","tid":208084,"uid":7612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"但俾祖記入兩波先 唔慌唔興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a117e35807c5edf4bbf2d30d0f8f67e0a36f1a","tid":208084,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T13:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但俾祖記入兩波先 唔慌唔興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今年巴塞歐聯主場只失了一球<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，祖記算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41411d593531794e2ce79cca4dab088c7df79fcc","tid":208084,"uid":7612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T20:27:05.000Z","msg":"睇到80分鐘 都仲爭3球 真興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd78802f71c85620f71af98db60624a712ead899","tid":208084,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T20:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到80分鐘 都仲爭3球 真興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p